item.title: Passive components for electronic circuits using conformal deposition on a scaffold
item.description: Precision fabrication of 3D objects is used for fabricating passive electrical components. A 3D scaffold is fabricated and then electrically conductive and/or insulating layers are deposited on the scaffold to form the electrical component.
